metadata.name: LazyApe#1
metadata.description: Lazy Apes is a limited collection of 333 uniquely designed digital characters PFP.  Rightful owner of Lazy Apes, holders will be granted an unlimited, worldwide, exclusive, license to use, copy, and display the purchased art for commercial use. They will be considered as a partner of this firm, they will be able to make further decisions regarding future projects and will be equal partners in regard of profit which will be distributed among the holders on the basis of number of Lazy Apes they have in their wallet. 50% of royalties will go to the charity, decided by holders.
